<h1>Claude Needham</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://www.xxaxx.com/now/">xxaxx.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Nevada City
CA
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
I have more than a few. During the course of a year I manage to spend a significant amount of time in each.  Artist & Stone Sculptor.  Writer – scifi, humor, transformational spirituality.  Web Developer – Galaxy Website Design.  Programmer – independent Xxaxxsoft.  Game designer – with GODD Games (resources, engine, level design).  Bassist – with Faxl.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I work as an “unorthodox bodhisattva”. Bodhisattva because wish is to help the liberation of all being everywhere. Unorthodox because I doubt anyone would agree that I'm going about it in the right way.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
Each of us, when we incarnated into this particular lifetime, had an intention, a goal, or task that we wished to accomplish. I walk the path I walk to discover my own life goals and help those who I am able do the same.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
My story is not my own, it is flavored by those I touch and those who have touched me. How I read this story is my real self.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
"The Story of My Experiments with Truth: An Autobiography" - by Mahatma Gandhi
</p>

